  "issue_title": "Add time-decay chart to PR details view",
  "issue_body": "## Summary\n\nAdd a PR time-decay chart to the PR details view that visualizes how the time-decay multiplier changes after merge and shows the current scored state in a compact, easy-to-read format.\n\n## Motivation\n\nPR scoring already includes time decay, but the current UI does not explain how that multiplier evolves over time. Users can see the current score, but not why it is lower than the original merged value or where the PR sits on the decay curve.\n\nA dedicated time-decay chart helps users understand:\n- when decay starts\n- how quickly score falls after merge\n- the current multiplier and score state at a glance\n\nThis improves transparency around scoring behavior and makes PR detail pages more informative for contributors tracking earned score over time.\n",
  "merged_at": "2026-04-30T01:54:44.000Z",
